00:58:58.622 --> 00:58:59.907
Take a seat.

755
00:59:23.171 --> 00:59:24.590
I'll take a look at that.

756
00:59:37.162 --> 00:59:38.700
How did this happen?

757
00:59:40.189 --> 00:59:42.438
I broke a cup.

758
00:59:47.352 --> 00:59:48.794
You need stitches.

759
00:59:52.202 --> 00:59:54.227
You do it for me, Doctor.

760
00:59:57.983 --> 00:59:59.642
Can you...

761
01:00:02.278 --> 01:00:05.231
let us sleep at your place tonight?

762
01:00:23.961 --> 01:00:30.961
Subtitles by DramaFever

763
01:00:41.697 --> 01:00:47.345
<i>[Call Me Mother / Mother]</i>

764
01:00:47.945 --> 01:00:49.430
<i>Why did you do it?</i>

765
01:00:49.530 --> 01:00:50.623
<i>Did you hate me?</i>

