767
01:00:53.327 --> 01:00:55.123
<i>Isn't that the least
you could do for me?</i>

768
01:00:55.123 --> 01:00:56.641
<i>Find the child first,
no matter what.</i>

769
01:00:56.641 --> 01:00:59.068
<i>Where are you, Hye Na?</i>

770
01:00:59.068 --> 01:01:00.840
<i>Why did she go to Iceland?</i>

771
01:01:00.840 --> 01:01:03.125
<i>Please don't try to learn
any more about us.</i>

772
01:01:03.125 --> 01:01:04.976
<i>Soo Jin has a child?</i>

773
01:01:05.438 --> 01:01:07.742
<i>Is a dangerous person after you?</i>

774
01:01:07.742 --> 01:01:09.974
<i>I want to go home, Mom.</i>

775
01:01:09.974 --> 01:01:11.353
<i>Our house.</i>

776
01:01:11.353 --> 01:01:13.559
<i>I will never see you again.</i>

777
01:01:13.559 --> 01:01:18.659
<i>Not all moms can raise a child.</i>

